2. **SDK Type Compatibility:** Third-party SDKs (like Mistral) may have stricter types than our generic interfaces - need adapter layer
3. **Browser vs Node Types:** setTimeout return types differ between environments - use `ReturnType<typeof setTimeout>` for cross-platform compatibility
4. **Modal Component API:** Should document enum values vs raw classes in component interfaces

